Subsection.Text: Every prepaid health clinic shall pay to the office the following fees:

Paragraph.Text: For filing a copy of its application for a certificate of authority or an amendment to such certificate, a nonrefundable fee in the amount of $150.
For filing each annual report, a fee in the amount of $150.

Subsection.Text: The fees charged under this section shall be distributed as follows:

Paragraph.Text: One-third of the total amount of fees shall be distributed to the Agency for Health Care Administration; and
Two-thirds of the total amount of fees shall be distributed to the office.
